OL,5, Labour has rowed back on its pledge to 
OL,6, invest #28bn a year in green industries
OL,7, if it wins power, saying it needs to be
OL,8, "responsible" with the public finances.
OL,10,FIn 2021 Labour promised to spend #28bn 
OL,11,Fa year until 2030 on green projects,   
OL,12,Ffunded by borrowing.                   
OL,14,FInstead shadow chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,15,Fsaid she would now ramp up investment  
OL,16,Fover time from a 2024 election win,    
OL,17,Freaching #28bn a year after 2027.      
OL,19,FShe told the BBC it was important not  
OL,20,Fto be "reckless" with spending.        
